factor out Source from Node
make it use a FileIO
move Text, Position etc. to a new module Source



sexp("I18n::t()") # =>
[:program,
 [:stmts_add,
  [:stmts_new],
  [:method_add_arg,
   [:call,
    [:var_ref, [:@const, "I18n", [1, 0]]],
    :".",
    [:@ident, "t", [1, 6]]],
   [:arg_paren, nil]]]]

watch the separator!



